-- Nikkei 225 Futures Fall After BOJ Policy Statement
-- B y   Y o s h i a k i   N o h a r a
-- 2013-08-08T03:00:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-08/nikkei-225-futures-fall-after-boj-policy-statement.html
Japanese stock futures fell after the
central bank issued a policy statement.  Nikkei 225 Stock Average futures traded in  Singapore 
climbed 0.6 percent to 13,940 as of 11:59 a.m. in  Tokyo . Before
the Bank of Japan announcement, the Nikkei 225 advanced 0.7
percent to 13,926.22 at the trading break in Tokyo. The broader
Topix index added 0.4 percent to 1,159.38.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yoshiaki Nohara in Tokyo at 
